ğŸ› ï¸ What is n8n?
n8n (short for "node-node") is a powerful open-source workflow automation tool that allows you to connect various services and automate tasks with little to no code. It acts like a visual editor where you build workflows using a drag-and-drop interface.

ğŸ”‘ Key Features
ğŸ”„ Low-code workflows: Build automations using nodes without writing code (but extendable with JavaScript functions when needed)

ğŸŒ Integrations: Supports 350+ apps like Gmail, Google Sheets, Slack, Notion, Webhooks, and APIs

ğŸ” Self-hostable: Unlike Zapier or Make, you can deploy n8n on your own server for full control and privacy

ğŸ“… Triggers and actions: Use scheduled triggers, webhook events, or app-specific events to kick off workflows

ğŸ” Conditional logic: Handle complex decision-making with IF, Switch, and Merge nodes

